title: joining champ select lobby late
body: anyone else getting this problem been happing to me for a while now and most the time only getting the last position and not even seeing if anyone else has called..

replies.body: happens to me a lot. I always thought it was just because I use a Mac (that's right, a MAC) {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
I get the same thing too, not entirely sure what the cause is. I hope the new champ select comes soon, because as much as I love support, it gets sickening.
